_aLatestUpdates._sText: This is the final release so any faults are permanent and i am sorry if there are glitches that weren't fixed.

_sText: This is the final version of Bhop_Consistancy. i extended it 3 rooms and my good buddy Aux made a bonus for this map which i enjoy. This map is a good 40 second speedrun with 7 rooms. It is not the greatest bhop map out there but i am personally very proud of this map and i hope people come to enjoy this map as much as i did making it. I will be uploading a video as soon as i get it. Thanks again to all the feedback from the last version and the help from others, enjoy.
